{"tid":889239,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【殘酷真相？】華為成中國製造驕傲？亞洲通訊社社長：是日本人研發的！","createTime":"2018-11-04T11:55:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T04:58:12.000Z","uid":125193,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"69610e9799b90880403d1cf7737d8d29ac77a51f","tid":889239,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T11:55:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/11/02/article/82038/?fbclid=IwAR2wvzI9u_KOtnAJpw6lQjVOIZTeYVkLikInvAokjapCaeMAXEQheMHSWq4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.presslogic.com%2F2018%2F11%2F02%2Farticle%2F82038%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2wvzI9u_KOtnAJpw6lQjVOIZTeYVkLikInvAokjapCaeMAXEQheMHSWq4&d=1ZBYsp%2FwIU%2BXG7hVFOcWV6NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=c7207464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/11/02/article/82038/?fbclid=IwAR2wvzI9u_KOtnAJpw6lQjVOIZTeYVkLikInvAokjapCaeMAXEQheMHSWq4</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>中國製造的內地手機品牌華為素來以其中國製造身份自豪，甚至外交部發言人華春瑩更曾經公開呼籲使用華為手機。雖然受到中國愛戴，但亞洲通訊社社長徐靜波卻公開表示華為是日本人研發的。</strong><br />\n<br />\n亞洲通訊社社長徐靜波日前出席於中國天津舉辦的第15屆中國製造業國際論壇，並發表演講。他在演講中表示，華為近年之所以發展蓬勃是因為有日本人研發，並採用了日本的技術。徐更指，日本除了研發華為技術外，更有為中國廠商提供零件。他大讚華為聰明，形容「把人家的頭腦買下來」。<br />\n<br />\n徐續指，聘請日本人除了薪酬比普通工資提高了約3分1外，華為更特意在日本設立研究所，並招聘了400個日本手機工程師一起開發新型手機。據悉，日本廠商亦會為OPPO、小米等廠商提供零件。華為的模式亦啓發了OPPO在日本設立自己的研究所。"},{"pid":"a683828811018d5b60cfe5cb1af90335e233db7b","tid":889239,"uid":35870,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到我即刻想買部華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1654c5ff1afa17d5b60053c3cfe1f8be63941aa1","tid":889239,"uid":209487,"like":3,"dislike":62,"score":-59,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T12:12:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad013924ab83556b27fc199cb0f7e5c0fb4b0b69","tid":889239,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,